>The role</STRONG><br><br><p style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Are you passionate about driving business growth and building strong client relationships?</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ready to join a global leader in software and cloud solutions?</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Want to leverage your sales expertise to empower organizations on their digital transformation journey?</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;\"> </p><p style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Join SoftwareOne’s high-performing sales team in Indonesia, collaborating with dedicated professionals focused on delivering value and innovation. We foster a culture of growth, integrity, and customer-centricity.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;\"> </p><p style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">As a Business Development Manager, you will identify and pursue new business opportunities, manage key client relationships, and drive revenue growth for SoftwareOne’s portfolio of Microsoft Licensing and Cloud Technology solutions. You will play a pivotal role in expanding market presence and supporting clients on their digital transformation journey.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;\"> </p><p style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Key Responsibilities: </strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;\"> </p><ul style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\"><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Identify and pursue new business opportunities in Microsoft Licensing and Public Cloud Technologies</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Achieve annual revenue and gross profit targets for the region</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Execute high-volume sales strategies targeting Mid-Market and Enterprise customers</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Present Microsoft MWP, Azure, and AWS propositions to prospects, collaborating with technical teams for closure</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Support marketing and sales teams in lead generation activities</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Provide expert guidance on licensing and  IT cloud solutions</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Prepare and present proposals, presentations, and reports to clients and senior management</span></li></ul> <br><STRONG>What we need to see from you</STRONG><br><br><ul><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Bachelor’s degree in Business, Marketing, or Information Technology and or related field</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Proven ability to develop and execute sales plans with resilience and objection handling skills</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Strong expertise in Microsoft business and Public Cloud Technologies</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Excellent communication, presentation, negotiation, and relationship-building skills</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Strong analytical and problem-solving capabilities</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ability to manage multiple projects and priorities independently and collaboratively</span></li></ul> <br><STRONG>Job Function</STRONG><br><br>Sales <br><STRONG>Accommodations</STRONG><br><br><div><em>SoftwareOne welcomes applicants from all backgrounds and abilities to apply. If you require reasonable adjustments at any point during the recruitment process, email us at </em><a href=\"mailto:reasonable.accommodations@softwareone.com\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"x_x_x_OWAAutoLink\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>reasonable.accommodations@softwareone.com</em></a><em>.   </em></div><div><em>Please include the role for which you are applying and your country location. Someone from our organization that is not part of the decision-making process will be in touch to discuss your specific needs and we will make every effort to accommodate you. Any information shared will be stored securely and treated in the strictest of confidence in line with GDPR.  </em></div><div><em>  </em></div><div><em>At SoftwareOne, we are committed to providing an environment of mutual respect where equal employment opportunities are available to all applicants and teammates without regard to race, color, religion, age, sex, national origin, disability status, genetics, protected veteran status, sexual orientation, gender identity or expression, or any other characteristic protected by federal, state, or local laws.  Additionally, we encourage experienced individuals that have taken an intentional career break and are now prepared to return to work to explore our SOAR program. </em></div> <ul><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Business, Marketing, or Information Technology and or related field</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Proven ability to develop and execute sales plans with resilience and objection handling skills</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Strong expertise in Microsoft business and Public Cloud Technologies</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Excellent communication, presentation, negotiation, and relationship-building skills</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Strong analytical and problem-solving capabilities</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ability to manage multiple projects and priorities independently and collaboratively</span></li></ul>"}
